cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Bit-Pop: A Proof-of-Concept Tool for Multi-Genome DNA Read Classification"
type: software
version: "0.1.0"
description: |
  A multi-genome DNA read classification tool that simultaneously maps
  sequencing reads against multiple reference genomes and identifies the
  best matching genome for each read. Combines FM-index-based k-mer filtering,
  2-bit XOR alignment, and Smith-Waterman refinement.
